step_data.thought: To check the customer order count, I need to navigate to the 'SALES' section in the Magento Admin Panel. Currently, I am on the Credit Memos page, which is part of the 'SALES' section. The next step is to go to the 'Orders' page, where the customer order count can typically be found. I will click on the 'SALES' link in the menu to access the relevant section.
